From 34d437a643b7461d0a64d90466e00ee346e0ba98 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Emergent E1 <emergent@example.com>
Date: Sat, 6 Jun 2026 11:05:43 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: email-or-username login, tap-to-move avatars, tap
 avatar to start DM

- Backend: /api/auth/login now accepts identifier (email OR username)
- Login UI: single Email or Username field
- DraggableMember: smooth spring animation to a controlled targetPosition;
  non-current users now tappable to start a private chat
- Room screen: tap on empty space inside the profile section to smoothly
  move your avatar to that spot; tap on another user's avatar to open the
  private chat with them pre-selected
- PrivateMessagesModal: accepts initialUserId prop to open a conversation
  with a specific user directly
- Backend fix: removed truncated avatar base64 placeholder that prevented
  the server from starting (now returns dicebear placeholder URLs)
---
